parameters:
Blacksmith Eleo: I'm in the middle of making a new piece!
Once it's finished, swing it around and give me your
feedback!

Clea: I have returned. I have completed greeting all the
allies who will help us reclaim the throne.

Guild Leader Agonia: Significant political movements create
chaos, but they also undoubtedly increase the opportunities
where our strength is needed.

Guild Leader Agonia: We continue to expect great things from
Clea's efforts.

\CL 【Guild Leader Agonia's Aftermath】Contributing to the
resolution of the chaos caused by the birth of King Rex,
Clea succeeds in once again gaining the trust of King Rex.

\CL She continued to demonstrate the way of adventurers to
her subordinates through her actions.

\CL Clea spent her life protecting the wings of freedom in
the Adventurer's Guild of Ftera. She remained loyal, never
lied, and never ran away, up until her death.

Stolge of Affection: I'm planning to hold a memorial
service for Shimos today, but let's make it a lively
celebration instead of a gloomy one!

Stolge of Affection: Even though he would refuse when
invited, once he started drinking, he was in a better mood
than anyone else.

\CL 【Stolge of Affection's Aftermath】After Agonia's
retirement, he assumed the position of Guild Leader of the
Adventurer's Guild. Although he said, I'm just a bridge, he
fulfilled his duties for over 10 years.

\CL She protected the guild using her expertise in
negotiation, which involved thoroughly adhering to the
principles of the Great Widow and Agonia, who advocated for
the weak and employing a skillful blend of firmness and
flexibility.

\CL His final words were, I'm going to have a wild party
with those who went before me.
Young female adventurer Ect: Welcome back, Clea-san!

Young female adventurer Ect: It's a selfish request, but...
can we talk together again in the dormitory courtyard?

\CL 【Aftermath of Young Female Adventurer Ect】She is a rare
researcher within the Adventurer's Guild and plays an active
role as the legitimate successor of her father, the digging
expert Melos.

\CL It was quite difficult to sort out my feelings towards
Clea, but I struggled and hesitated many times, and
sometimes even fought against her.

\CL Nevertheless, I continued to maintain a close
relationship with Clea throughout my life.

Blacksmith Elero: How are your weapons holding up? I'll fix
them right away.

\CL 【Aftermath of Blacksmith Elero】Because Clea and the
others helped fulfill my dreams, I continued to maintain and
repair their weapons free of charge while I was still
active.

\CL Due to his personality, he had a hard time finding
disciples, but after being scolded by Clea and Piste, he
started making efforts to train his successor.

\CL He loved weapons, lived for weapons, and remained active
until the end.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Receptionist Piste: Oh? A visitor, I wonder?
Receptionist Piste: Yes, I'm coming right now~!
Clea: Guild Master, regarding the escort of King Rex--

Receptionist Piste: E-Everyone! Something terrible has
happened!

Guild Master Agonia: Could it be that something has happened
to King Rex?

Receptionist Piste: It's an invitation, an invitation! From
Celis-chan to Clea-chan!
Clea: Let's fulfill the promise we made that day.
Clea: I'll be waiting for you at the Adventurer's Cave.
Guild Master Agonia: Clea, go and fulfill your promise.

Guild Master Agonia: Even if there is something that doesn't
sit right with you, there must be something to gain from
meeting with Celis.

Guild Master Agonia: If you don't go, you will definitely
regret it. This is not the advice of a guild master, but
rather the meddling of an old man.
Clea still doesn't know, does she?

Guild Master Agonia: That's why I called them. Their
relationship was special even within the guild.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
実績 はじまりの場所

Guild Leader Agonia: Do you remember the words from that
time?

Clea: Who am I...? I have been living while constantly
pondering that question until today.

Clea: However... I still don't have an answer. It feels like
there's something missing, something that I can truly be
satisfied with.

Guild Leader Agonia: The strictness towards oneself, that is
both Clea's virtue and flaw.

Guild Leader Agonia: I may be able to give you an answer,
but I also understand that you will never be satisfied with
it.

Guild Leader Agonia: I feel like I've started to see the
answer that I should come up with myself.

Guild Leader Agonia: I believe that you will take shape
while protecting someone's daily life, as you mentioned
before.

Clea: I will not betray, lie, or run away. Through the
requests of the adventurer guild Futeira, I will find the
answer.

Stolge of Affection: The stench of the usurped throne still
lingers around King Lex. This might just be the beginning
once we enter the entrance.
Stolge of Affection: Are you expecting something from Clea?
Clea: Yes, I will strive to meet your expectations.

Receptionist Piste: It's hard to believe, but now there are
many people who care about Clea-chan, even though she used
to give off an unapproachable vibe.

Receptionist Piste: And I'm glad that there are also many
people who care about her just as much. Let's continue to
work hard together at the Adventurer's Guild!

Clea: I might have relied on you the most. Once again,
please take care of me in the future requests as well.
